		<td width="100%" class="newssubject" colspan=2><a name="news_5482"></a>
Fix your EQ rep for only $50<br>
			<font class="smallcomments">[ <a href="/forums/showthread.php?threadid=5482" class="smallcommentshi">6 comments</a> ] submitted by: Bloodshard</font><br>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="15">&nbsp;</td>
		<td>
<br>
<i>From Castersrealm </i><br>
<br>
HAVE AN IDENTIY CRISIS?<br>
<br>
Sony has introduced a new system by which you can change your players name!<br>
Starting from $49.95 you can have you characters first name and surnames changed provided you can prove ownership of the account (Legends subscribers still get this service for free).<br>
<br>
The new service is somewhat unexpected considering that the policy until now has been to only change first names if they violated the Naming Policy. We contacted SOE regarding the reasoning behind the change and they stated they will respond in the near future.<br>
<br>
If you are interested in a new identity for any of your characters you can access the official website for more details</td>
	</tr>
